### A: GET
GET http://localhost:8080/todo/1

### B: GET
GET http://localhost:8080/todo/1

### B: PUT（先に実行）
PUT http://localhost:8080/todo/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "更新B",
  "done": false,
  "version": 8
}


### A: PUT（後で実行 → 409）
PUT http://localhost:8080/todo/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "更新A(ロック想定)",
  "done": false,
  "version": 8
}


### POST 
POST http://localhost:8080/todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "新規ToDo",
  "done": false
}